<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<!-- Include the head of the EJS. Contains the meta tags and stylesheet link -->
<%- include("./partials/head") %>

<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">

<!-- Include the header. Common style applies -->
<%- include("./partials/navbar") %>

<!-- ----------------------------------- BEGINNING OF THE BODY OF THE PAGE ----------------------------------------- -->
<div class="container mt-5" id="page-body">

    <h1 class="text-center mt-2">Welcome to Placement Hub!</h1>
    <h4 class="text-center">Empowering Student Placements Through Community, Affordability, and Support</h4>

    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="mt-5 carousel slide rounded">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner rounded">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="images/student-accommodation-cut.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="student accommodation">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Accommodations</h5>
                    <p>Find just the perfect accommodation for your placement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="images/forum.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="placement forum">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Forum</h5>
                    <p>The best place to discuss anything about your placement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Find Affordable Accommodation</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">We know how expensive housing can be, especially when you're on a student
                            budget. That's why we've gathered a variety of affordable accommodation options near your
                            placement location. Whether you're looking for hospital accommodation, a private room or
                            want to split costs with a roommate, our platform has got you covered. </p>
                        <a href="/map" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Accommodation</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Ask questions and share insights</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Need answers? Our placement forum is the place to go. Ask your questions
                            and get straight-to-the-point responses from students who have been through it all. Share
                            your own experiences and insights to help others navigate their placements. Plus, you'll
                            have access to a wealth of placement-related resources to help you succeed.</p>
                        <a href="/forum" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Forum</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Connect with Peers Nearby</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Placement can be lonely, but it doesn't have to be. With PlacementHub
                            Social, you can find and connect with students at your placement location. Organize
                            meetups, study groups, or just hang out and unwind. Building a strong support network is
                            key to making the most of your placement experience, and PlacementHub Social makes it easy
                            to do just that.</p>
                        <a href="" class="btn btn-primary disabled">Coming soon</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
<!-- --------------------------------------- END OF THE BODY OF THE PAGE ------------------------------------------- -->

<!-- Include the footer. Common style applies -->
<%- include("./partials/footer") %>

<!-- Include the scripts-->
<%- include("./partials/scripts") %>
</body>
</html>